<h2 class="bold font-l">The White Hats</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The Cheese Guild, informally known as the White Hats, rule Cheesebridge like a fiefdom and hold tastings of the finest cheeses. They're known for their tall white hats. </p>
</div>
